Name: FIND YOUR WINGS
About the game: HAVE YOU RECIEVED A CALL FROM 1-800-GET-WING? When someone loses their wings, we reach out. If you ever get a call from us then you may have lost your wings. It happens. In FIND YOUR WINGS you'll be: Shooting relentless squares that keep multiplying and getting stronger Buying upgrades for your gun, and debuffs for your enemies Increasing your defense with many, many supporters such as snipers, sawblades, tesla coils and black holes- and many more Finding different wings that give you cool, special abilities FIND YOUR WINGS has 4 stages for you to beat, and a freeplay mode where you can set your own rules.
